overview: Pregnancy can be seen as one of the most important journeys of a woman's life, but for Tan Kaili, it has always been a source of pressure and stress. But being in the minority is not an easy journey. One day, when life gets her down, Kaili decides to pretend to be pregnant to see if there is solace on the other side. What ensues is a journey of discovery, adventure, and even love.
title: Baby Bumps
